headline: Why J. M. Smucker (SJM) Shares Are Sliding Today
summary: Shares of packaged foods company J.M Smucker (NYSE:SJM) fell 4.1% in the afternoon session after Argus downgraded the stock to Hold from Buy, citing concerns over volume growth.
